485
01:56:55,041 --> 01:56:56,301
Mi pequeño.

486
01:59:03,001 --> 01:59:05,401
¿Vas a quedarte ahí plantado?

487
02:00:17,881 --> 02:00:20,211
La única manera de ser feliz es amando.

488
02:00:24,881 --> 02:00:26,681
Si no sabes amar,

489
02:00:28,791 --> 02:00:30,981
